    <p>You use this keyword to specify the color of a field on a color display.</p>
  <li>The transparent keyword is used to make a color transparent. This is often used to make a transparent background color for an element. </li>
  <li>The transparent keyword is used to make a color transparent. This is often used to make a transparent background color for an element. </li>
  <li>The inherit keyword specifies that a property should inherit its value from its parent element.</li>
