<div class="content">
  <p>In HTML, we use the button tag to create a button, but by using CSS properties, we can style the buttons. Buttons help us to create user interaction and event processing. They are one of the widely used elements of web pages.
    <br>CSS pagination is a very useful technique for indexing different pages of a website on the homepage. If your website has lots of pages, you have to add some sort of pagination to each page.
  </p>
  
</div>
